  "body": "**Is this a bug report or feature request?**\r\n* Feature Request\r\n\r\n**What should the feature do:**\r\n\r\nSupport device filtering with udev DEVLINKS names, e.g. `/dev/disk/by-path/pci-.*-sas-.*`.\r\n\r\nRelated issue and pull request:\r\n\r\n* https://github.com/rook/rook/issues/1228\r\n* https://github.com/rook/rook/pull/2845\r\n\r\nThough the issue above is similar to mine, the related pull request does not support regular expressions.\r\n\r\n**What is use case behind this feature:**\r\n\r\nI want to select disks for OSDs by their `/dev/disk/by-path/...` name patterns.\r\nThis enables to use predictable and topology-aware device names.\r\n",
